column5: Cute single bedroom available in house less than 10 minutes to downtown and 5 from green belt! Has a large backyard to relax quiet mornings by a dry bed. Located in a quiet cul de sac. Full beautiful kitchen and bathroom two steps from room. Fully loaded with towels, bed sheets, toiletries, and some house warming surprises! Dogs do live on property, very well behaved.
column8: Cozy bedroom in the heart of south Austin!
